repoDetails.name: radiant
repoDetails.description: Radiant is a no-fluff, open source content management system designed for small teams.

repoDetails.name: radiant-extension-registry
repoDetails.description: A web service to support the distribution and installation of extensions for Radiant CMS.

repoDetails.name: radiant-prototype
repoDetails.description: Prototype of the user-interface of Radiant CMS.

repoDetails.name: radiant-trac
repoDetails.description: Trac support files for the Radiant CMS development site.

repoDetails.name: radiant-wiki
repoDetails.description: Support files for the Radiant CMS wiki.

repoDetails.name: radiant-artwork
repoDetails.description: Artwork assets for Radiant CMS

repoDetails.name: radiant-mockups
repoDetails.description: Mockups of the Radiant CMS user-interface.

repoDetails.name: radiant-website
repoDetails.description: Support files for the Radiant CMS website.

repoDetails.name: radiant-aggregation-extension
repoDetails.description: An extension for Radiant CMS to collect the children of unrelated pages for iteration with <r:children:each>.

repoDetails.name: radiant-import-export-extension
repoDetails.description: An extension for Radiant CMS to support importing and exporting data between the database and YAML.

repoDetails.name: radiant-page-attachments-extension
repoDetails.description: An extension for Radiant CMS to support file uploads modeled as attachments to pages.

repoDetails.name: radiant-search-extension
repoDetails.description: An extension for Radiant CMS to support searching pages.

repoDetails.name: radiant-event-calendar-extension
repoDetails.description: Create, organise and display calendar events in your radiant site. Read, aggregate and serve ical subscriptions.

repoDetails.name: radiant-ldap-extension
repoDetails.description: An extension for Radiant CMS to support access to LDAP directories.

repoDetails.name: radiant-related-content-extension
repoDetails.description: An extension for Radiant CMS to support relating pages to one another arbitrarily.

repoDetails.name: radiant-share-layouts-extension
repoDetails.description: An extension for Radiant CMS that allows controllers to render their views within Radiant layouts.

repoDetails.name: radiant-link-roll-extension
repoDetails.description: An extension for Radiant CMS that lets you create link rolls, or lists of favorite links.

repoDetails.name: radiant-reorder-extension
repoDetails.description: An extension for Radiant CMS that allows you to specify and change the order of child pages within their parent page.

repoDetails.name: radiant-mailer-extension
repoDetails.description: An extension for Radiant CMS that allows you to create 'contact us' and other mail-bound forms.

repoDetails.name: radiant-multi-site-extension
repoDetails.description: An extension for Radiant CMS that lets you serve multiple sites (domains) from a single instance.

repoDetails.name: radiant-scheduler-extension
repoDetails.description: An extension for Radiant CMS that lets you specify date/times for pages to appear and expire (disappear).

repoDetails.name: radiant-twitter-extension
repoDetails.description: An extension for Radiant CMS to send notifications of newly published pages to a Twitter account.

repoDetails.name: radiant-api
repoDetails.description: A simple ActiveResource-based API for Radiant.

repoDetails.name: radiant-sns-extension
repoDetails.description: Adds Stylesheet and Javascript management to Radiant

repoDetails.description: German translations for Radiant CMS bundled with the main application.
